## Installation

###  pip
Install from [PyPi](https://pypi.org/project/file-renamer/)
```bash
# Install
pip install file-renamer

# Run
file-renamer
```

1. Tested on Fedora Linux Workstation 40 & Windows 11
1. macOs and other operating systems not tested (may the gods be with you!)


